<title>laminas-validator</title>
<indexterm><primary>laminas-validator</primary></indexterm>

<para><anchor xml:id="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2laminas_2laminas-validator_2_r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md6437"/> <link xlink:href="https://github.com/laminas/laminas-validator/actions/workflows/continuous-integration.yml"></link> <link xlink:href="https://coveralls.io/github/laminas/laminas-validator?branch=master"></link></para>

<para>laminas-validator provides a set of commonly needed validators. It also provides a simple validator chaining mechanism by which multiple validators may be applied to a single datum in a user-defined order.</para>
<section xml:id="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2laminas_2laminas-validator_2_r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md6438">
